 This  program check validation of the volumes at startup.
 Copy "valid" to the C: dir, insert "C:valid QUIET" somewhere in
 your startup-sequence (after setpatch) and reset the computer.

 CLI template:  LANGUAGE/K,QUIET/S
   LANGUAGE - program messages language (OS 2.1+)
              ( .catalog file must be installed in LOCALE:CTALOGS dir)
              buildin - english
   QUIET    - no comment

